------------------------------------------------------------------
------------------ Beaufort_ROMS_waves_sedfluxes -----------------
------------------------------------------------------------------

This repo contains analysis scripts used for the manuscript 
"The Influence of Waves on Open Water Suspended Sediment Fluxes 
on the Alaskan Beaufort Sea Shelf: A Numerical Modeling Study" that
is in review at JGR Oceans (as of 10/15/2025).

Updates:
- Repo created (10/15/2025)
